data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! This gem will impress the moment you step inside, from the light-filled living room to the spacious kitchen with island breakfast bar. Upstairs find the spacious master suite, 2 additional bedrooms, and a great loft/living area to use as office space, playroom or cozy up for a movie. Owners installed sleek upgrades throughout including new flooring, blinds, and remote-controlled fans and lights. You’ll appreciate the generous living spaces & ample storage. Located in a lovely neighborhood near Manette with/ easy access to the Seattle Ferry, downtown Bremerton and just a short walk to the YMCA. This home is immaculate throughout. Pride in ownership shows here! Motivated Sellers!
